    @Public
public class ScalaAggregateOperator<IN>
extends org.apache.flink.api.java.operators.SingleInputOperator<IN,IN,ScalaAggregateOperator<IN>>
    This operator represents the application of a "aggregate" operation on a data set, and the result data set produced by the function.
